# Node Category

## Definition

A Node Category describes the semantic category of a Node.

## Specification

Every Node MUST declare exactly one Category.

The declared Category MUST exist in the Schema.

The Category determines which Edge types are valid for the Node.

A Category SHOULD describe the purpose of the knowledge, not its storage location.

## Example

```
category: requirement
```

